reviewText: Love all of these movies so it was an awesome deal, three movies for the price of one in the stores.
This is every teens wet dream for movies. Well maybe not these days with all the porn on the internet, but these movies are super funny and definitely worth every penny. Underrated movies for sure

Not a lot to say about these classics.  You either love them, or hate them.  While I love Porky's and Bachelor Party, I watch PCU most often...

Excellent on-line purchase experience...

I brought this for PCU, I had loved the movie when it came out and wondered if it was still any good - or one of those movies you watch again and think 'oh no!?!?'

However it turned out to just as good as I remember and the other two movies are very funny bonus'.

I totally love all of these classics. All three are timeless, and lots of fun to watch. These classics will live on for a long time. I purchased this DVD for my 22 yr. old son, whom is a fan of both Porkys as well as the Batchelor Party/PCU. This is a must see.
